<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.9.1">
<l>mūvaril muṉmutal vaṉmuḻaṅ kārkaṭa luḷkiṭantu</l>
<l>pūvula runtitaṉ ṉuḷpuva ṉampaṭait tuṇṭumiḻnta</l>
<l>tēvarkaḷ nāyaka ṉaittiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>kōvalar kōvinta ṉaikkoṭi yēriṭai kūṭuṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will the one with the creeper-like waist join Govinda of the cowherder,</l>
<l>Who stands in Tirumāliruñcōlai, leader of the gods,</l>
<l>The first and foremost among the Three who, having created the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">in his navel where a flower burgeoned,</l>
<l>Sleeping in the full, roaring sea, ate [and] expelled [it]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
